post_text: (For Fri. Sep 11th) Due to continued poor air quality, we will not be delivering food on Friday. The daycare will be closed as well. School is in session so please have your students "attend" their online classes. The district office will be closed to visitors and there will be no Chromebook pick up. Classified staff, please check in with your supervisors.

post_text:
(For Thu. Sep 10th) Due to continued poor air quality, we will not be delivering food on Thursday. Additionally, the food share has been canceled.
The daycare will be closed as well.
School is in session so please have your students "attend" their online classes.
The district office will be closed to visitors and there will be no Chromebook pick up.
Classified staff, please check in with your supervisors.

Nick Krupke KPTV
February 4, 2019 at 9:00 PM ·

Cheers to 50 years at Gervais High School in the athletic record books for the one and only, Miss James. The Cougar Hall of Famer and all-time great librarian, Jeannine James. 'It's the kids. I've been single all of my life and the school was the center of my life and it still is.' - FOX 12 Oregon https://www.kptv.com/news/a-lifelong-court-ship-retired-gervais-hs-librarian-still-keeping/article_be8cdca8-28f8-11e9-8963-338248d1a462.html

post_text: We will be closing school one hour early due to the weather. Buses will begin loading students at GES at noon and will move on to load students at the other schools after that. post_text: We will be closing school one hour early today due to the weather. Buses will begin loading students at GES at noon and will move on to load students at the other schools after that. Please arrange to pick up your student(s) at noon or to meet them at home when their bus arrives.
text: We will be closing school one hour early today due to the weather. Buses will begin loading students at GES at noon and will move on to load students at the other schools after that. Please arrange to pick up your student(s) at noon or to meet them at home when their bus arrives.

post_text: Latchkey and all afternoon activities are cancelled today due to the weather. The school day will continue on its regular schedule for Wednesday, which is an early-release day already. This message will be updated as necessary if the situation changes.
text: Latchkey and all afternoon activities are cancelled today due to the weather. The school day will continue on its regular schedule for Wednesday, which is an early-release day already. This message will be updated as necessary if the situation changes.
